@startuml
actor User
participant "Browser UI" as UI
participant "Express API" as API
participant "Auth Service" as Auth
database "SQLite" as DB

User -> UI : submit login form
UI -> API : POST /api/auth/login
API -> Auth : validate credentials
Auth -> DB : find user by email
DB --> Auth : user record
Auth -> Auth : compare password hash
Auth --> API : JWT + user
API --> UI : 200 OK + token
UI -> UI : store token
UI -> API : GET /api/dashboard\nAuthorization: Bearer token
API --> UI : dashboard payload
@enduml
